title: #82 Nalick Trupp "Eskimo Libertarian"
subtitle: #82 Nalick Trupp "Eskimo Libertarian"
summary:
Nalick Trupp joins the show this week from the Mat-Su valley in Alaska. She is a member of the Yup'ik tribe and over the last two years she has become politically active. Also known as "Eskimo Libertarian" across social media we take a wild ride through what it's like living and eating in the far north and some really interesting cultural differences that I didn't know about.
